Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:09.69,Episode Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Episódio 3\N{\fs22}Imprevisível
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:13.08,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Eles estão aqui de verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.22,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:17.74,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Personagens que sempre aparecem \Nem escolas de anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:20.23,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Aquelas duas são gêmeas, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:23.71,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,A que nasceu primeiro é mais ativa \Ne a mais nova é quieta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:26.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Está falando de Takanashi-san \Ne Ninomae-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:27.75,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Elas não são gêmeas. Nem irmãs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.23,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Quê? Não?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:32.52,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi-san não é arteira o suficiente \Npara ser chamada de ativa,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:35.36,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,e a Ninomae-san não é tão quieta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:38.26,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Certo... E a menina com cabelo cacheado?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:40.46,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Ela deve ser muito rica, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.59,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Ela não tem noção do valor do dinheiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:44.94,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,nunca foi ao supermercado ou ao karaokê!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:45.82,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuzumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:49.70,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Ela é da minha sala. O pai dela \Nnão é rico nem pobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:50.51,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:53.02,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Ela disse que recebe 5.000 ienes de mesada.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:54.51,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:58.74,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Koharun, você não vai achar \Npersonagens definidos na escola.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:01.82,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,É... Você está certa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:05.01,Main Dialogue,Mobuko,0000,0000,0000,,O quê? Como "se" abrevia "soy sauce"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:07.35,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,"So" para "miso" é um exemplo também.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:10.40,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Mas elas são três grupos de sêxtuplas \Ncom um ano de diferença.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:13.24,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,E-Elas são as mais fáceis de definir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:13.22,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Bem, vamos pensar em um novo clube hoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:15.62,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Que tal começarmos com um clube cultural hoje?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:16.42,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Boa ideia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.24,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Que tal o grupo de shogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Shogi, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:20.95,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Que imagem eles têm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:21.71,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Simplórios.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:23.14,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.50,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,A imagem que eu tenho é que eles são quietos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:26.67,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,E quando eles falam,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:29.60,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,você pensa, "nossa, então essa é a sua voz!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:33.11,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,E não tem sempre dois ou três encrenqueiros?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.45,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Que são muito preguiçosos para \Nentrar em um clube atlético,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:37.32,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,mas querem entrar em algum clube,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:40.47,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,então escolhem o clube de shogi\N por ser só um jogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.45,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:45.12,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,E os outros membros ficam irritados com eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:50.16,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,É como se fossem duas partes, \Nos jogadores sérios e os barulhentos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:52.31,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Deve ser difícil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:56.72,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Os nomes das estratégias não são \Ndesnecessariamente legais?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Tipo... "Sistema Fujii",
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:02:59.85,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,"Especial Tsukada",
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,"Carruagem Voadora"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:02.30,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,"Matador de Ogro",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.34,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,"Ouro Sem Igual",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:04.45,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,"Milênio"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.71,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Vários nomes pretensiosos, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:08.83,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Como vocês sabem tanto assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.16,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Eles arrumam as peças de um jeito legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:14.38,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Eles batem as peças, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:17.82,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Até na sala eles batem as borrachas \Ndaquele jeito na mesa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:19.63,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,E quando pagam com moedas no mercado,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.71,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,batem as moedas no balcão.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:24.37,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Quê? Existe gente que faz isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:27.85,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Quando aprenderam tudo isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:31.20,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Koharun, não se diz "pôr uma peça" no shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:31.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.81,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ao falar isso a um membro do clube de shogi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:38.97,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,ele te olharia torto, "no shogi falamos {\i1}colocar{\i0}, \Nnão {\i1}pôr{\i0}", então tenha cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:42.52,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Ele resmungaria, dizendo \N"não misture shogi com mahjong!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:46.37,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Uma conversa dessas nunca vai acontecer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:50.42,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,E em mangá e anime? Que imagem vocês têm deles?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:54.32,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,O lugar costuma ser uma escola de \Ntreinamento com nome de "fundação".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.33,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,É mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.57,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Tem sempre um personagem grosso
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:04:00.01,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,em um mundo que valoriza boas maneiras.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sim! Ele veste roupas casuais e um boné.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,E no tatâmi ele senta com um joelho para cima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:08.11,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,E é o personagem que joga muito bem
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.96,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,e da sua própria maneira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:14.52,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Sempre tem alguém que consegue \Nfalar com as próprias peças.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.95,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Já vi isso! Já vi isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:18.27,Shogi Sign,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Não tenha medo!\NVá em frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:18.27,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Durante a partida as peças começam a brilhar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.97,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Diferente dos clubes atléticos, \Nas partidas são individuais,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:24.18,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,e eles competem em um lugar \Ncalmo e sem conversa,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.10,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,então eles precisam dessa postura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:29.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,E usam lugares pequenos de 2m².
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.93,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Por isso que certos mangás usam a expressão
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:34.67,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,jogadores "imersos no jogo".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.33,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Já vi isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:39.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Koharun, o que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:42.77,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Estou assustada com o conhecimento que \Nvocês têm de shogi em mangá...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:44.84,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Não é nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:48.11,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Certo, agora que já compartilhamos \Na imagem que temos do clube de shogi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.85,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,vamos inventar um "clube de shogi diferente"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.81,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Quem tiver uma ideia, fale!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.88,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Ok... Yua.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:57.07,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Eu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:58.31,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Eu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.74,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Ok! Eu falo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:02.33,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Um "clube de shogi diferente"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.44,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Todas as peças são placas de promessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:07.80,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Placas de promessa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.06,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Aquelas onde escrevem pedidos?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:09.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:13.41,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,As peças têm pedidos escritos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:19.40,Shogi Sign2,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Que a cirurgia da minha             Que haja paz no mundo.\Nmãe corra bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.27,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Tipo "Que haja paz no mundo"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:19.03,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ou "Que a cirurgia da minha mãe corra bem".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.05,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.86,Shogi Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,Que a cirurgia da minha\Nmãe corra bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.23,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Se a peça for tomada, o pedido não se realiza?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.15,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Provavelmente.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.17,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Que pressão!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:29.58,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Então se a peça "que a cirurgia da \Nminha mãe corra bem" for tomada...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:30.85,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Essa não pode ser tomada.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:31.57,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Certo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:32.82,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Seria a peça mais forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.44,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sim. É novo, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.78,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,É novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.78,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}É novo, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.50,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Me dá uma dor no coração.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.04,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, mais alguém?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:40.86,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:43.47,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Certo, Aoi. Vamos lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.86,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Seu "clube de shogi diferente"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:50.32,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Os jogadores ficam despedaçados... \NPor causa das peças.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.43,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Era para ser um trocadilho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.23,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:52.87,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,É novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.32,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,É novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:56.57,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,É novo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.89,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Eu não tinha pensado nisso.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.29,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Eu só quis falar isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.78,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,"Os jogadores ficam despedaçados" \Nnão tem um significado especial?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:03.79,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.89,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Mas existem jogadores que \N"ficam despedaçados", né?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:07.84,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.89,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Falou quando a conversa já estava morrendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.35,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Isso é tão Aoi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:11.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}É mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:15.80,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Você tentou ajudar Aoi-chan, mas só piorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:19.68,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sim. Ok, quem é a próxima?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:20.39,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.81,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Koharun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.82,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, um "clube de shogi diferente"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.28,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Eles tentam mover as peças com a outra mão!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.64,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Faz diferença?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.76,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Deveria.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.01,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}É mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:33.08,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Acho que seria mais difícil colocá-las,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.83,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,então os jogadores ficariam alterados.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.00,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:39.75,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,É novo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.61,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,É novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:44.85,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Todo mundo passa por uma fase \Nde querer ser canhoto, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.97,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Hã? Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:46.97,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}É verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:47.92,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,É?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.35,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Já aconteceu comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:49.38,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.38,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.45,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.59,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Eu comia com a mão esquerda
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:56.30,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,e falava que eu era ambidestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:57.88,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Me esforçava só para isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.39,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,É mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.41,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,As pessoas têm isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.42,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Vocês passaram por isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:02.89,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:03.86,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uau...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.81,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,O que acha, Hiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.16,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Bem, se tentar no shogi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:10.86,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,acho que não faria tanta diferença...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:11.98,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Não, talvez te ajude a vencer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.82,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Pode mudar o curso do jogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:14.38,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:16.47,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Você disse isso com bastante propriedade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.35,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Quem é a próxima?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.30,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:23.92,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, o "clube de shogi diferente" da Hiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.00,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Tem muito mais drama que o necessário.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:30.69,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,O lanceiro é o irmão mais novo da torre oponente,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:42.33,Drama Sign 1,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Torre
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:42.33,Drama Sign 2,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Lanceiro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:42.33,Drama Sign 3,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Prata
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:42.33,Drama Sign 4,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Ouro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:33.43,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,ou o general de prata está saindo \Ncom o general de ouro oponente...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.43,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Está falando das peças?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.50,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,As peças!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:36.98,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:38.67,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Não está falando dos jogadores.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:39.55,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Não.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.32,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,As peças!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:42.33,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,As peças têm sua própria história.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.13,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.62,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Seria difícil de jogar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.07,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Seria, mas é novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Você colocaria sua peça com a história em mente.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:52.13,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Pensaria "não posso colocar esses dois juntos",
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:54.47,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,poderia ser até uma lição de moral.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.61,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:59.13,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,"Talvez se eu colocar aqui, esses dois se reconciliem..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.25,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Talvez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.30,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,É novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.41,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Pensem nisso, apesar do nosso clube não ser oficial,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:07.98,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,é surpreendente como usamos \Na quadra normalmente.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:12.78,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-senpai faz parte de vários comitês, \Nentão ela tem vantagens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.49,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Tchãnã!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:18.34,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Uau, um shogi gigante!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:21.33,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,O clube de artes fez para mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:24.55,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Clubes científicos e artísticos têm muito talento
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.29,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,nesse tipo de escola.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:27.24,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.39,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Obrigada, Mobuko-chan e irmãs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.94,Main Dialogue,Mobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Boa sorte!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.80,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,O que faremos com isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.35,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Eu fiquei inspirada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:37.49,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Pensei em fazer uma combinação entre shogi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.00,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,e algum jogo popular de anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.38,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Jogo popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Fiquem no meio do tabuleiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:47.04,Spinner Sign 1,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mão Esquerda      Mão Direita
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:47.04,Spinner Sign 2,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Pé Esquerdo      Pé Direito
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:47.04,Spinner Sign 5,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Rei      Ouro
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:47.04,Spinner Sign 10,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Bispo      Peão
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:47.04,Spinner Sign 11,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Lanceiro                                Torre
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:47.04,Spinner Sign 12,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Prata                              Cavalo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.52,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Eu vou primeiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.21,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi, mão esquerda, 7-6, peão.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.27,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Mão esquerda. Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:55.61,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, mão esquerda, 8-4, peão.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:59.10,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Mão esquerda, 8-4... Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:02.14,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Espera, isso é Twister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.01,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:05.99,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Certo, Aoi, mão direita, 6-8, torre.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.31,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Torre, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:07.93,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Pronto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:10.68,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Koharun, pé direito, 3-4, peão.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:11.53,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Meu pé?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.71,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,E-Essa é difícil...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.27,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Se cair, você perde.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:16.09,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.09,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Koharun, por que está virada para cá?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.33,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,O inimigo está para lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.34,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Só segui suas instruções, Hiina-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:26.35,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Pé esquerdo, 7-8, peão, coma uma peça.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:27.94,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Não consigo ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:31.55,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,E não consigo virar a peça com meu pé!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:34.22,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Essa é difícil...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.52,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Não consigo mais ficar aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:36.77,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Sem pensar demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.41,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Como ficamos assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.56,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Não sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.38,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Certo, Koharun, a jogada final!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.48,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Mão direita, 3-8, ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.99,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,3-8...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.09,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,A bunda da Aoi-senpai está no caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.57,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Não consigo colocar o general de ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.67,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,E eu a teria em xeque-mate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.57,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi, belo bloqueio!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.34,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:59.75,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Koharun, passe pelo vão de algum jeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:00.66,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:07.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ok! Hiina e Koharun perderam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:10.52,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Isso nem parece shogi!
